room_title: Escape room "Unsolved Murder Mystery" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: First time in an escape room. Me and my three daughters from Chicago tried to unsolved mystery room. We made it with 1.33 left. It was closed and super fun.

review: Super awesome place! We did the murder mystery room. Had a great time! It's something very different and fun to do. Definitely going back to do the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Unsolved Murder Mystery" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: This was so much fun! I took my 11-year-old son, and we had a blast. We did the murder mystery and escaped with 48 seconds left on the clock!! The staff was super friendly. I can't wait to try one of their other rooms.
